== 主题 ==
[[File:Bruce_Willis_by_Gage_Skidmore.jpg|thumb]]还是争取到了这个机会。]]

[[吕克·贝松|吕克·贝松]]在接受采访时表示，《第五元素》虽然有重要的主题，但并非一部“主题宏大的电影”。他希望能让观众对片中莉露的一句台词感同身受：“如果自己都不珍惜，那挽救生命又有什么意义？”<ref name="stephen" />杰伊·托雷特（{{lang|en|Jay P. Telotte}}）在《科幻电影》（{{lang|en|''Science Fiction Film''}}）一书中称，本片探讨了[[政治腐败|政治腐败]]的主题<ref>{{cite book | last = Telotte | first = J. P | year = 2001 | title = Science Fiction Film | url = http://books.google.com.hk/books?id=izKtL3IFBXcC&pg=PA16&dq=science+fiction+themes+%22fifth+element%22&hl=en&sa=X&ei=7VbFUdmqBcS0iQfCjoCoAw&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=science%20fiction%20themes%20%22fifth%20element%22&f=false&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr | publisher = Cambridge University Press | isbn = 978-0-521-59647-3 | page = 16 | accessdate = 2014-12-08}}</ref>。

布莱恩·奥特（{{lang|en|Brian Ott}}）和艾里克·青木（{{lang|en|Eric Aoki}}）在女权杂志《女性传播学研究》（{{lang|en|''Women's Studies in Communication''}}）发文，认为性别也是本片的主要主题之一。两位作者批评电影开场后很长时间都没有女性出场，前20分钟里唯一的女性形象就是经重建诞生的莉露，或许还有总统身边那位男女不分的助手。片中出场的其他女角要么过分性感化，如空姐和[[麦当劳|麦当劳]]服务员；要么就没有任何传统女性特征，比如艾斯伯格（{{lang|en|Iceborg}}）少校<ref name="women">{{cite journal | last1 = Ott | first1 = Brian L | last2 = Aoki | first2 = Eric | year = 2001 | title = Counter-Imagination as Interpretive Practice: Futuristic Fantasy and The Fifth Element | journal = Women's Studies in Communication | publisher = Taylor & Francis | volume = 27 | issue = 2 | pages = 149–176}}</ref>。斯特凡·勃兰特（{{lang|en|Stefan Brandt}}）在《颠覆阳刚》（{{lang|en|''Subverting Masculinity''}}）一书中也认为电影中对女性的描绘“充斥着性别方面的刻板印象”，即便女主角莉露也不例外。在勃兰特看来，莉露也只有在与孟加罗人肉搏时那2分10秒才摆脱了那种被动的人物形象，其他戏码里，无论是片头掉进男主角的出租车，还是片尾追问科本对自己的情意，她都是一般的无助、渴望依赖达拉斯的男子氣概。除小汤姆·利斯特扮演的总统以外，电影中的其他男性角色都通过各种手段来尽可能表现得缺乏男子氣概，例如既婆妈又柔弱的鲁比·罗德、笨拙的维托·维托科尼利厄斯，以及愚蠢的蒙罗将军等，这都是为了通过对比，来让充满男子氣概的科本散发出“神一般”的光芒。<ref>{{cite book | last = Brandt | first = Stefan | chapter = American Culture X: Identity, homosexuality, and the search for a new American hero | title = Subverting Masculinity: Hegemonic and Alternative Visions of Masculinity in Contemporary Culture | editor1-last = West | editor1-first = Russell | editor2-last = Lay | editor2-first = Frank | year = 2000 | pages = 67–93 | publisher = Rodopi | location = Amsterdam | isbn = 978-90-420-1234-9}}</ref>

苏珊·海沃德（{{lang|en|Susan Hayward}}）在《吕克·贝松电影》（{{lang|en|''The Films of Luc Besson''}}）一书中表示，《第五元素》就是一个男人“从部落中脱颖而出，证明自己的男子氣概、战胜邪恶势力并杀死其首脑，最终获得保障和婚姻作为奖励”的经典故事<ref name="Hayward-2009" />{{rp|98}}。在海沃德看来，科本的征程不但受到佐格和孟加罗人的威胁，连莉露都是他成功路上的阻碍，后者直到最后一刻才变得顺从并向他提供帮助，接受他爱的表白<ref name="Hayward-2009" />{{rp|98}}。爱情是《第五元素》的剧情主线之一，并且和保卫宇宙生命的主线有同样紧迫的期限<ref name="Hayward-2009" />{{rp|98}}。海沃德还认为，[[生态学|环境破坏]]问题也是电影的重要主题，片中[[垃圾|垃圾]]和污染随处可见<ref name="Hayward-2009" />{{rp|91-92}}。就[[科幻片|科幻片]]而言，未来世界失控是很常见的事，往往有一些新的科技或威胁超越人类，或是威胁到人性的存在，不过《吕克·贝松电影》一书还是将《第五元素》列入少数“竖起一面镜子”、展现出人类负责任一面的科幻电影之列<ref name="Hayward-2009" />{{rp|92}}。海沃德觉得影片对[[资本主义|资本主义]]和[[消费主义|消费主义]]提出质疑，佐格办公室里的小工具让他对技术的渴望显得如同一种恋物癖<ref name="Hayward-2009" />{{rp|92}}。电影把人和科技之间的紧张关系当成一种需要彻底解决的问题来处理<ref name="Hayward-2009" />{{rp|92}}。

== 制作 ==
[[File:Milla_Jovovich_2013.jpg|thumb]]
贝松早在少年时代就曾设想《第五元素》中的世界来打发时间，他从16岁时就开始编写剧本，但电影要一直到他38岁才在院线上映<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.allmovie.com/movie/the-fifth-element-v154944 | title = The Fifth Element (1997) | work = AllMovie | accessdate = 2014-12-09 | archivedate = 2014-08-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140804003851/http://www.allmovie.com/movie/the-fifth-element-v154944}}</ref>。据贝松所说，他打算在拍摄本片前先树立起作为[[导演|导演]]的声誉，这样自己就能够拥有创意上的主控权<ref name="stephen" />。

贝松和[[布鲁斯·威利斯|布鲁斯·威利斯]]早在电影开拍数年前就见面探讨过这一项目，但导演之后打算改请一位相对来说更年轻也更默默无闻的男演员来扮演科本，所以他把更多时间花费在选址、服装和特技效果上而非演员身上。威利斯之后联系贝松，表示自己仍然有意出演，导演于是告知自己在选角上的想法，威利斯于是答复：“吕克，你懂的，如果我有意的话，我们总会想到办法。”为了出演这个角色，威利斯还与摄制剧组达成了协议，此举让贝松大为赞赏。<ref name="stephen" />曾与贝松在《[[这个杀手不太冷|这个杀手不太冷]]》中合作过的[[加里·奥德曼|加里·奥德曼]]获聘饰演佐格，导演称赞奥德曼是“世界上最优秀的5位演员之一”<ref name="stephen" />。贝松为了给莉露找到合适的演员而亲自面见了200到300名申请人，最终入选的是[[米拉·乔沃维奇|米拉·乔沃维奇]]<ref name="stephen" />。

{{Quote|从物理特征方面来说，米拉这人很多样化，她既可以来自过去，也可能源于未来。她或者是古埃及或古罗马人，也可能是[[娜芙蒂蒂|娜芙蒂蒂]]或是从外太空来的。我很喜欢她的这种特点。|吕克·贝松<ref name="stephen" />}}

麦温·勒·贝斯柯在片中出演迪娃，她和贝松在电影开拍前已经相恋6年，但在本片拍摄期间，贝松离开了贝斯柯同乔沃维奇在一起<ref name="maiwen">{{cite web | url = http://anthemmagazine.com/film-critic-maiwenns-polisse/ | title = Film Critic: Maïwenn's 'Polisse' | last = Change | first = Kee | date = 2012-05-05 | work = Anthem Magazine | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141208052359/http://anthemmagazine.com/film-critic-maiwenns-polisse/ | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2014-12-09 | archivedate = 2014-12-08}}</ref>，两人之后成婚，但又在1999年离婚<ref name="H&Q">{{cite journal | last = Buys | first = Sara | title = Milla's Tale | date = 2003-01 | work = Harpers & Queen | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141026085410/http://www.millaj.com/art/harpersqueen0103.shtml | archivedate = 2014-10-26 | url = http://www.millaj.com/art/harpersqueen0103.shtml | accessdate = 2014-12-09}}</ref>。

贝松本期望能在[[法国|法国]]拍摄本片，但由于无法找到合适的地点而不得不“怀着一颗沉重的心”改在[[伦敦|伦敦]]取景<ref>{{cite web | title = Paris prosecutors probe Luc Besson's 'Film City' studios | date = 2013-12-20 | work = Hürriyet Daily News | accessdate = 2014-12-09 | archivedate = 2014-11-29 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141129041056/http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/paris-prosecutors-probe-luc-bessons-film-city-studios.aspx?pageID=238&nID=59891&NewsCatID=351 | url = http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/paris-prosecutors-probe-luc-bessons-film-city-studios.aspx?pageID=238&nID=59891&NewsCatID=351}}</ref>。具体拍摄地点包括[[皇家歌剧院|皇家歌剧院]]<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.roh.org.uk/news/top-films-featuring-opera-20-16 | title = Top films featuring opera 20-16 | last = Shipman | first = Chris | date = 2011-10-11 | website = Royal Opera House | accessdate = 2014-12-09 | archive-date = 2014-11-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141116111132/http://www.roh.org.uk/news/top-films-featuring-opera-20-16 | dead-url = no }}</ref>和[[松林制片厂|松林制片厂]]的[[007片场|007片场]]<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.pinewoodgroup.com/production/fifth-element | title = The Fifth Element  | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141113111819/http://www.pinewoodgroup.com/production/fifth-element | work = Pinewood Studios | accessdate = 2014-12-09 | archivedate = 2014-11-13 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。片中的[[埃及|埃及]]实际上是在[[毛里塔尼亚|毛里塔尼亚]]取景<ref name="shay">{{cite journal | last = Elrick | first = Ted | year = 1997 | title = Elemental Images | url = http://books.google.com.hk/books?id=RWcqAQAAIAAJ&q=cinefex+%22fifth+element%22+mauritania&dq=cinefex+%22fifth+element%22+mauritania&hl=en&sa=X&ei=FXdmVJb1BeG6mAWE6oKoCg&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr | journal = Cinefex | issue = 70 | pages = 130 | accessdate = 2014-12-09}}</ref>。不过，《第五元素》虽然主要是在伦敦拍摄，但仍属法国电影之列<ref name="faber" /><ref name="Mazdon-2000" />，并且耗资数额也刷新了欧洲电影的历史纪录<ref name="alice" />。法国漫画制作人[[尚·吉罗|尚·吉罗]]和让-克洛德·梅济耶尔共同担任电影的艺术指导设计师<ref name="av">{{cite web | url = http://www.avclub.com/article/rip-moebius-comics-legend-and-imetal-hurlant-ico-f-70686 | title = R.I.P. Moebius, comics legend and Métal Hurlant co-founder | last = Heller | first1 = Jason | date = 2012-03-10 | work = The A.V. Club  | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141111072039/http://www.avclub.com/article/rip-moebius-comics-legend-and-imetal-hurlant-ico-f-70686 | archivedate = 2014-11-11 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2014-12-09}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141111071418/http://io9.com/5922655/luc-besson-adapting-classic-time-travel-comic-created-by-fifth-element-concept-artist | deadurl = yes | title = Luc Besson adapting classic time-travel comic created by Fifth Element concept artist | last = Anders | first = Charlie | date = 2012-07-01 | work = io9 | accessdate = 2014-12-09 | url = http://io9.com/5922655/luc-besson-adapting-classic-time-travel-comic-created-by-fifth-element-concept-artist | archivedate = 2014-11-11 }}</ref>。两人的漫画作品对电影中未来纽约市的影像有着举足轻重的影响<ref name="Bizony-2001">{{cite book |last=Bizony |first=Piers | year = 2001 | title = Digital Domain: The Leading Edge of Visual Effects |url=https://archive.org/details/digitaldomainlea0000bizo | location = London | publisher = Aurum Press | isbn = 978-0-8230-7928-5}}</ref>{{rp|169}}。梅济耶尔创作的《力量的循环》（{{lang|en|''The Circles of Power''}}）中有位名叫斯特拉克斯（{{lang|en|S'Traks}}）的角色，在外星球的一个庞大城市中开出租车为生，并且出租车是在天上飞行，空中的交通还很拥堵。梅济耶尔把这本书寄了份给贝松，后者深受启发，把科本·达拉斯由原本的火箭船厂工人改为出租车司机，并且纽约也变成一个空中到处都是各种交通工具飞来飞去的模样<ref name="Mézières-2004" />。纽约的建筑物既受到20世纪60年代[[代谢运动|代谢运动]]风格大型模块化公寓的启发，又受到该世纪10年代建筑师安东尼·圣伊利亚（{{lang|en|Antonio Sant'Elia}}）的未来风格设计影响<ref name="Hanson-2005">{{cite book | last = Hanson | first = Matt | year = 2005 | title = Building Sci-Fi Moviescapes: The Science Behind the Fiction | location = Waltham, Massachusetts | publisher = Focal Press | isbn = 978-0-240-80772-0}}</ref>{{rp|65}}。贝松要求片中的大部分动作戏都要在白天发生，他对科幻电影中常见的黑暗飞船走廊和昏暗行星深感厌烦，想让《第五元素》摆脱这样的模式，看起来更光亮，“高高兴兴、疯疯颠颠的”，哪怕那些阴沉的镜头更为现实<ref name="Bizony-2001" />{{rp|169}}。法国时尚设计师[[让-保罗·高缇耶|让-保罗·高缇耶]]设计了本片中的服装<ref name="cbs">{{cite web | url = http://www.cbsnews.com/news/jean-paul-gaultier-fashions-wild-child/ | title = Jean Paul Gaultier: Fashion's wild child | last1 = Teichner | first1 = Martha |date = 2012-01-22 | work = CBS News | accessdate = 2014-12-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141021083156/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/jean-paul-gaultier-fashions-wild-child/ | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-10-21}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | archivedate = 2014-11-11 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141111050825/http://www.tribuneindia.com/2011/20110708/ttlife1.htm | url = http://www.tribuneindia.com/2011/20110708/ttlife1.htm | title = Flirting with change | last = Sehajpal | first = Ashima | date = 2011-07-08 | work = The Tribune | accessdate = 2014-12-09}}</ref>。据苏珊·海沃德所说，高缇耶的设计属于对传统知性的侵犯<ref name="Hayward-2009" />{{rp|96}}，颠覆性和性别的固有准则<ref name="Hayward-2009" />{{rp|104}}。高缇耶还借用他人的作品作为辅助，以达到自己想要的效果<ref name="Hayward-2009" />{{rp|104}}。

鲁比·罗德一角起初名叫洛克·罗德（{{lang|en|Loc Rhod}}），电影的原创剧本和改编小说中都出现了这个名字<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.cnet.com/au/news/the-404-yuletide-mini-sode-where-the-404-is-the-fifth-element/ | title = The 404 Yuletide Mini-sode: Where The 404 is the Fifth Element | last = Yu | first = Justin | date = 2009-12-28 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141014135521/http://www.cnet.com/au/news/the-404-yuletide-mini-sode-where-the-404-is-the-fifth-element/ | archivedate = 2014-10-14 | deadurl = no | work = CNET | accessdate = 2014-12-09}}</ref>。有评论估计，这一名字的更改是对[[元素周期表|元素周期表]]中信息的发挥。鲁比源自[[第5周期元素|第5周期]]的第一种元素[[铷|铷]]（{{lang|en|Rubidium}}），而罗德（{{lang|en|Rhod}}）则源自同样属第5周期的[[铑|铑]]（{{lang|en|Rhodium}}），该元素的位置正好在第5周期正中，人物的姓名就由两种元素的前半截组成<ref name="Hayward-2009" />{{rp|89}}。还有评论中称，此人名源于其性别混淆的个人特点，虽然有男性化的姓氏，但配上的却是女性的名字<ref name="women" />。“鲁比·罗德”的英文“{{lang|en|ruby rhod}}”也指第一台可用[[激光|激光]]机的关键组成部分<ref>{{cite book | last = Townes | first = Charles | year = 2003 | title = A Century of Nature: Twenty-One Discoveries that Changed Science and the World | location = Chicago, USA | publisher = University of Chicago Press | pages = 107–112 | isbn = 0-226-28413-1}}</ref>。

片中莉露所说的“神国语言”纯属[[虚构语言|虚构]]，只有约400个词，由贝松和乔沃维基创作。两人还在现实生活中用这种语言交谈、写信来练习。<ref>{{cite book | last = Rogers | first = Stephen D | date = 2011-11-15 | title = The Dictionary of Made-Up Languages: From Elvish to Klingon, The Anwa, Reella, Ealray, Yeht (Real) Origins of Invented Lexicons | url = http://books.google.com.hk/books?id=fA5NhKLOxdYC&pg=PA51false&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | publisher = Adams Media | page = 51 | isbn = 978-1-4405-2817-0 | accessdate = 2014-12-09}}</ref>
[[File:Fifth_Element_Circles_of_Power.png|thumb]]（上图）是受到《[[力量的循环|力量的循环]]》系列漫画（下图）启发<ref name="Mézières-2004">{{cite book | last1 = Mézières | first1 = Jean-Claude | last2 = Christin | first2 = Pierre | year = 2004 | others = Trans. Timothy Ryan Smith | title = Valerian: The New Future Trilogy | url = https://archive.org/details/valeriannewfutur0001chri | series = Valérian: Spatio-Temporal Agent | publisher = iBooks | location = New York | chapter = The Circles of Power | isbn = 978-0-7434-8674-3 | page = [https://archive.org/details/valeriannewfutur0001chri/page/65 65]}}</ref>]]

=== 特技效果 ===
电影的特效制作由[[数字领域|数字领域]]公司完成，卡伦·古勒卡斯（{{lang|en|Karen Goulekas}}）获聘为数字效果总监<ref name="Bizony-2001" />{{rp|131}}。数字领域采用的软件包括{{lang|en|[[PowerAnimator|Alias]]}}<ref name="shay" />、{{lang|en|[[Softimage|Softimage]]}}、{{lang|en|Arete}}、{{lang|en|Side Effect's Prisms}}、{{lang|en|[[PhotoRealistic_RenderMan|RenderMan]]}}和内部软件<ref name="Hanson-2005" />{{rp|60}}。部分镜头采用了真人演出、[[比例模型|比例模型]]、[[计算机成像|计算机成像]]和[[粒子系统|粒子系统]]共同完成<ref name="Bizony-2001" />{{rp|28}}。片中纽约市的空中交通场景就是用粒子系统创建。
{{Quote|text=我们有约80个城市景观的镜头，其中加上计算机成像制作的汽车四处飞驰，每个镜头里的东西都太多了，你根本不可能完全靠手工完成……汽车转弯时会自动变速，所以[[动画师|动画师]]不需要操心这点。他们只需在非常固定的空间内描绘动作，数字技术会把其他工作搞掂。——卡伦·古勒卡斯<ref name="Bizony-2001" />{{rp|140}}}}

片中纽约市的建筑采用比例模型拍摄。技术人员以1比24的比例制作了数十幢公寓楼和25幢摩天大楼，其中一些有6.1米高<ref name="Bizony-2001" />{{rp|173}}。这些模型的制作一共耗费了80名工作人员5个月的时间<ref name="Bizony-2001" />{{rp|173}}。这些工作人员表示，建筑物窗户的制作是最费时的工作之一，特别是窗户后面需要反映出来的细节，如家具、窗帘、灯箱广告和尺寸很小的平面艺术作品<ref name="Bizony-2001" />{{rp|173}}。为了增强微缩模型的真实感，特效团队还需在数字环境中建立虚拟场景<ref name="Hanson-2005" />{{rp|64}}。所有模型镜头都是采用[[运动控制摄影|运动控制摄像机]]摄制，镜头收集到的数据导出后可用于追踪和生成计算机动画，并应用到粒子系统中<ref name="Hanson-2005" />{{rp|65}}。电影制作过程中还采用了数字[[接景|亚光绘画]]背景<ref name="Bizony-2001" />{{rp|106}}，一些动画的数字模型还应用了[[非均匀有理B样条|非均匀有理B样条]]，例如莉露的身体在纽约实验室中重建的那段镜头<ref name="Bizony-2001" />{{rp|139}}。

=== 配乐 ===
苏珊·海沃德认为《第五元素》一定程度上又是贝松的[[音乐剧|音乐剧]]风格电影<ref name="Hayward-2009" />{{rp|44}}，全片约有90分钟存在某种形式的配乐<ref name="Hayward-2009" />{{rp|47}}。本片[[电影配乐|配乐]]由[[艾瑞克·塞拉|艾瑞克·塞拉]]作曲，他大量采用管弦乐曲，例如片中[[科学家|科学家]]和[[外科医生|外科医生]]准备重建莉露时响起的[[双簧管|双簧管]]和弦乐曲，以及正在重建时采用的弦乐拨弦演奏。塞拉的音乐还受到多种异国风情的影响，如片中太空港桥段的[[斯大林主义|斯大林式]]号角，飞机起飞前的[[雷鬼音乐|雷鬼音乐]]段落，还有游客到达豪华游轮时演奏欢迎宾客前来的[[草裙舞|草裙舞]]音乐。<ref name="Hayward-2009" />{{rp|68}}片中也有更为常规的音乐形式，如第五元素的[[主导动机|主导动机]]段落就是在片头帕科利教授提及第五元素时首次响起；战舰准备攻击恶魔的黑暗星球时，背景中响起了穷兵黩武般的军鼓；莉露从电脑上得知[[战争|战争]]的存在时，观众可以听到[[古斯塔夫·马勒|马勒]]的葬礼进行曲<ref name="Hayward-2009" />{{rp|68}}。片中出租车和警车追逐段落的音乐由[[阿尔及利亚|阿尔及利亚]]艺人[[哈立德_(音乐家)|哈立德]]（{{lang|en|Khaled}}）创作，名为“{{lang|en|Alech Taadi}}”<ref>{{cite book | last = Cornea | first = Christine | title = Science Fiction Cinema: Between Fantasy and Reality | url = http://books.google.com.hk/books?id=OF-jcN8vbXEC&pg=PA207&dq=Khaled+%22Alech+Taadi%22+%22fifth+element%22&hl=en&sa=X&ei=8zOOUcrELoiViAfrm4CwDg&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=%22Alech%20Taadi%22&f=false | year = 2007 | publisher = Rutgers University Press | isbn = 978-0-8135-4173-0 | page = 207 | accessdate = 2014-12-10}}</ref><ref name="Hayward-2009" />{{rp|53}}，这段音乐没有包含在电影的原声带中，不过可以在哈立德的唱片“{{lang|en|N'ssi N'ssi}}”中找到<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.allmusic.com/album/nssi-nssi-mw0000112685 | title = Khaled: N'ssi N'ssi | last = Sheridan | first = Tim | work = AllMusic | accessdate = 2014-12-10 | archivedate = 2013-06-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130621195145/http://www.allmusic.com/album/nssi-nssi-mw0000112685}}</ref>。

片中迪娃表演的唱段包含[[葛塔诺·多尼采蒂|葛塔诺·多尼采蒂]]创作的《[[拉美莫尔的露琪亚|拉美莫尔的露琪亚]]》第3幕第2场选段《那柔和的声音》（{{lang|it|''Il dolce suono''}}）<ref name="Gemini">{{cite web|title=Gemini Sun Records is Proud to Announce Vitas |work=Press release |publisher=Gemini Sun Records |url=http://vitas.com.ru/gemini_press_release_eng.htm |accessdate=2014-12-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130729164445/http://vitas.com.ru/gemini_press_release_eng.htm |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2013-07-29 }}</ref>，是片中为数不多的几段带有歌词叙述呈现的音乐之一<ref name="Hayward-2009" />{{rp|45}}。虽然迪娃一角是由法国女演员麦温·勒·贝斯柯饰演<ref name="maiwen" />，但这首歌曲的演唱者实际上是阿尔巴尼亚[[女高音|女高音]]歌唱家[[英瓦·穆拉|英瓦·穆拉]]（{{lang|en|Inva Mula}}）<ref>{{cite web | archivedate = 2012-06-20 | url = http://www.allmusic.com/album/the-fifth-element-virgin-mw0000020753 | title = The Fifth Element [Virgin] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120620213230/http://www.allmusic.com/album/the-fifth-element-virgin-mw0000020753 | work = AllMusic | accessdate = 2014-12-10| deadurl = no}}</ref>。电影中的这首咏叹调在《第五元素》的原声带上分成两部分，第一部分题为《拉美莫尔的露琪亚》，第二部分题为《迪娃之舞》（{{lang|en|''The Diva Dance''}}），两段曲目正好是上下曲，第一段的结束紧接着第二段的开始，以求达到像电影中那样平稳过渡，一气呵成的效果<ref>{{cite AV media | people = éric Serra | date = 1997-05-06 | title =The Fifth Element | medium = Soundtrack | publisher = Virgin Records}}</ref>。

《第五元素》的原声带由[[维京唱片|维京唱片]]发行，在[[公告牌二百强专辑榜|《公告牌》二百强专辑榜]]上最高排到第99位<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.allmusic.com/album/the-fifth-element-virgin-mw0000020753/awards | title = The Fifth Element [Virgin] – Awards | work = AllMusic | accessdate = 2014-12-10 | archivedate = 2014-12-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141210024235/http://www.allmusic.com/album/the-fifth-element-virgin-mw0000020753/awards | deadurl = no}}</ref>。唱片持续时间约为63分钟，单在法国就售出了超过20万份<ref name="Hayward-2009" />{{rp|43-44}}。罗德尼·巴德多夫（{{lang|en|Rodney Batdorf}}）在{{lang|en|[[Allmusic|Allmusic]]}}网站上给予唱片三星评价（最高五星），称其表现“包罗万象、多才多艺，在电影以外也像电影中那样效果十足”<ref name="all">{{cite web | url = http://www.allmusic.com/album/the-fifth-element-original-motion-picture-soundtrack-mw0000020753 | title = The Fifth Element [Original Motion Picture Soundtrack] | last = Batdorf | first = Rodney | work = AllMusic | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141210024843/http://www.allmusic.com/album/the-fifth-element-original-motion-picture-soundtrack-mw0000020753 | archivedate = 2014-12-10 | accessdate = 2014-12-10}}</ref>。{{lang|en|Filmtracks.com}}网站上的一篇评论同样给予唱片三星评价（最高五星）<ref name="filmtracks" />。

== 发行 ==
=== 初步上映 ===
《第五元素》在[[第50届戛纳电影节|第50届戛纳电影节]]首映，并且是这届电影节的开幕片<ref name="festival-cannes.com">{{cite web | url = http://www.festival-cannes.com/en/archives/ficheFilm/id/4789/year/1997.html | title = Festival de Cannes: The Fifth Element | work = Cannes Film Festival | accessdate = 2014-12-09 | archivedate = 2014-11-11 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141111051123/http://www.festival-cannes.com/en/archives/ficheFilm/id/4789/year/1997.html}}</ref>。[[高蒙电影公司|高蒙]]搭建了面积超过9300平方米的放映区，来宾可以得到一块“第五元素”[[斯沃琪|斯沃琪]]手表，并以此作为门票入场观看电影。现场还有未来风格的芭蕾舞表演，让-保罗·高缇耶的时装演出，以及焰火表演。高蒙为此次活动约花费了100到300万美元，创下戛纳电影节的新纪录。<ref>{{cite web|deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140715010638/http://variety.com/2013/film/features/the-fickle-fetes-1200466152/ |archivedate=2014-07-15 |url=http://variety.com/2013/film/features/the-fickle-fetes-1200466152/ |title=Cannes parties are legendary, but sometimes the shindig can outperform the pic |last=Gray |first=Timothy |date=2013-05-13 |work=Variety |accessdate=2014-12-09 }}</ref>

=== 票房 ===
本片在美国上映的第一个周末就进账1700万美元，登上票房榜冠军宝座<ref name="faber" />。电影获得了商业上的成功，全球票房超过2.63亿美元，几乎是9000万美元预算的3倍<ref name="mojo" />。美国市场贡献了《第五元素》总票房的26%<ref name="mojo" />，在1997年的世界电影中，本片收入排名第9<ref name="mojo" />，是这年法国的电影票房冠军<ref name="Mazdon-2000" />，该国观影人数超过769万<ref name="Hayward-2009" />{{rp|91}}。电影在德国获得金银幕奖，这表明本片在该国售出了超过300万张电影票<ref>{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141105211353/https://www.goldene-leinwand.de/filme/das-fuenfte-element/?articles%5Bsearchvalue%5D=Element | archivedate = 2014-11-05 | url = https://www.goldene-leinwand.de/filme/das-fuenfte-element/?articles%5Bsearchvalue%5D=Element | title = Das fünfte Element | work = Goldene Leinwand | accessdate = 2014-12-09}}</ref>。《第五元素》刷新了法国电影的票房纪录<ref name="alice"/>，保持了16年后才被[[2011年电影|2011年]]的《[[无法触碰_(法国电影)|无法触碰]]》打破<ref name="intouchable">{{cite web | url = http://www.ozap.com/actu/-intouchables-plus-gros-succes-de-l-histoire-pour-un-film-non-anglophone/440005 | title = 'Intouchables': plus gros succès de l'histoire pour un film non-anglophone | date = 2012-03-21 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006092854/http://www.ozap.com/actu/-intouchables-plus-gros-succes-de-l-histoire-pour-un-film-non-anglophone/440005 | work = PureMédias | accessdate = 2014-12-09 | archivedate = 2014-10-06 }}</ref>，并且作为其他国家和地区收益最高法国电影的地位仍然保持<ref name="palmer">{{cite book | last = Palmer | first = Tim | title = Brutal Intimacy: Analyzing Contemporary French Cinema | year = 2011 | publisher = Wesleyan University Press | isbn = 978-0-8195-6827-4 | page = 116 | accessdate = 2014-12-09 | url = http://books.google.com.hk/books?id=neyI_geiqksC&pg=PA116&dq=%22fifth+element%22+expensive+french&hl=en&sa=X&ei=uLGUUb-hFuKiigfcuYDABg&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=%22fifth%20element%22&f=false&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr}}</ref>。

=== 专业评价 ===
[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]上收集了58篇针对本片的专业评论文章，其中41篇给出“新鲜”的正面评价，“新鲜度为”71%；网站上的共识评价这样写道：“视觉上创意十足而且让人赏心悦目，吕克·贝松的《第五元素》是部自始至终没有太把自个儿当回事儿的神奇流行科幻电影”<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/fifth_element/ | title = The Fifth Element Movie Reviews, Pictures | work = Rotten Tomatoes | accessdate = 2014-12-09 | publisher = Flixster | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141027120333/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/fifth_element/ | archivedate = 2014-10-27}}</ref>。而{{lang|en|[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]}}上收集的22篇评论文章中则有10篇好评，3篇差评，9篇褒贬不一，综合得分52（最高100）<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-fifth-element | title = The Fifth Element | work = Metacritic | accessdate = 2014-12-09 | publisher = CBS Interactive | archivedate = 2014-11-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141102072740/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-fifth-element}}</ref>。

《第五元素》上映后所获评价趋于两极化。《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》的凯文·托马斯（{{lang|en|Kevin Thomas}}）描述电影是场“制作精良到甚至有些做作的科幻盛会，几乎像去年的《[[碟中谍|碟中谍]]》一样难以模仿”。他在总结中称，《第五元素》会远比观众期望的更加温暖、风趣，并且包括有一些最为精良和机智的制作及服装设计<ref>{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141108011617/http://articles.latimes.com/1997-05-09/entertainment/ca-56892_1_fifth-element | url = http://articles.latimes.com/1997-05-09/entertainment/ca-56892_1_fifth-element | title = 'Element': A Voyage as Fun, Stylish as It Is Confusing | last = Thomas | first = Kevin | date = 1997-05-09 | work = Los Angeles Times | accessdate = 2014-12-10 | archivedate = 2014-11-08 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。[[罗杰·埃伯特|罗杰·埃伯特]]和吉恩·西斯克尔（{{lang|en|Gene Siskel}}）都在影评节目《[[看电影_(美国电视剧)|看电影]]》（{{lang|en|''At the Movies''}}）中给予本片“大拇指向上”的好评<ref>{{cite episode | title = Week of May 10, 1997: ''The Fifth Element'' review | series = At the Movies | airdate = 1997-05-10 | season = 11 | number = 35}}</ref>，埃伯特还在《[[芝加哥太阳报|芝加哥太阳报]]》的专栏上给予电影三星评价（最高四星），称这是部“伟大的愚蠢电影”，他在总结中这样写道：“我不会错过这部电影，它影像的丰富程度也值得我推荐。但从127分钟的片长来说，虽然看起来还算合理，但还是有些太长了”<ref name="roger" />。

部分影评对电影夸张的格调不满并予以严厉的批评。托德·麦卡锡（{{lang|en|Todd McCarthy}}）在《[[综艺_(杂志)|综艺]]》杂志上写道：“《第五元素》是各种元素组成的大杂烩，没法恰如其分地凝聚到一块儿，很大程度上来说，这是欧洲试图制作美国式科幻巨制，最终沦为东施效蹙的作品”<ref name="todd" />。《{{lang|en|[[Slate_(杂志)|Slate]]}}》杂志的大卫·埃德尔斯坦（{{lang|en|David Edelstein}}）用辞更为尖刻，称“这到底是不是有史以来最糟糕的电影或许很难说，但这就是最精神错乱的电影之一”<ref name="slate" />。

影评人对克里斯·塔克饰演鲁比·罗德的演出看法也是两极分化<ref>{{cite web | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141109173640/http://www.newsweek.com/motor-mouth-man-172650 | archivedate = 2014-11-09 | url = http://www.newsweek.com/motor-mouth-man-172650 | title = Motor Mouth Man | date = 1997-09-07 | work = Newsweek | accessdate = 2014-12-10}}</ref>。《洛杉矶时报》<ref>{{cite web | archivedate = 2014-07-15 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140715044255/http://articles.latimes.com/1997-05-08/entertainment/ca-56524_1_luc-besson | url = http://articles.latimes.com/1997-05-08/entertainment/ca-56524_1_luc-besson | title = In His Element | last = Smith | first = Steven | work = Los Angeles Times | accessdate = 2014-12-10 | deadurl = no}}</ref>和《[[时代_(杂志)|时代]]》周刊给予好评，《时代》还称他是“这年夏天最离谱的特技效果”<ref>{{cite journal | year = 1998 | title = Chris Tucker | magazine = Los Angeles | accessdate = 2014-12-10 | issue = November | pages = 96 | url = http://books.google.com.au/books?id=4V0EAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA96&dq=%22luke+perry%22+%22fifth+element%22&hl=en&sa=X&ei=kUSSUeOpEYeQiAf094GwCA&ved=0CFkQ6AEwCQ#v=onepage&q=%22luke%20perry%22%20%22fifth%20element%22&f=false}}</ref>。不过，《[[全面电影|全面电影]]》（{{lang|en|''Total Film''}}）的乔什·温宁（{{lang|en|Josh Winning}}）则认为，塔克的表演是本片的薄弱环节，他在评选“50个毁掉电影的表演”时把塔克在《第五元素》中的演出排名第20位<ref>{{cite web | accessdate = 2014-11-02 | title = 50 Performances That Ruined Movies | first = Josh | url = http://www.totalfilm.com/features/50-performances-that-ruined-movies/chris-tucker-the-fifth-element-1997 | last = Winning | date = 2011-11-02 | work = Total Film | archivedate = 2014-11-02 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141102025130/http://www.totalfilm.com/features/50-performances-that-ruined-movies/chris-tucker-the-fifth-element-1997}}</ref>。

=== 影响和相关媒体 ===
多种出版物认为《第五元素》是科幻[[邪典电影|邪典经典]]电影<ref name="cbs" /><ref>{{cite web | title = Milla Jovovich on Resident Evil And Her Ultraviolet Beef | last = Yamato | first = Jen | date = 2007-08-13 | work = Rotten Tomatoes | accessdate = 2014-12-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141030091431/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/resident_evil_extinction/news/1662363/milla_jovovich_on_resident_evil_and_her_ultraviolet_beef/ | archivedate = 2014-10-30 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/resident_evil_extinction/news/1662363/milla_jovovich_on_resident_evil_and_her_ultraviolet_beef/}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://io9.com/5663948/luc-bessons-next-film-is-the-fifth-element-to-the-power-of-ten |title=Luc Besson's next film is 'The Fifth Element to the power of ten' |last=Woerner |first=Meredith |date=2010-10-14 |work=io9 |accessdate=2014-12-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120807183748/http://io9.com/5663948/luc-bessons-next-film-is-the-fifth-element-to-the-power-of-ten |archivedate=2012-08-07 }}</ref>，但也有尖锐批评的声音，要求贝松“他妈的离科幻远点儿”<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.timeout.com/london/film/the-100-best-sci-fi-movies | title = 50 essential sci-fi films – part two | last = Huddleston | first = Mark | work = Time Out | accessdate = 2014-12-10 | archivedate = 2014-10-21 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141021221933/http://www.timeout.com/london/film/the-100-best-sci-fi-movies }}</ref>。据影评人[[马克·克默德|马克·克默德]]（{{lang|en|Mark Kermode}}）所称，《第五元素》是他的读者存在分歧最大的电影，既有些认为这是有史以来最优秀的暑期大片，也有人认为这是最糟糕的。克默德回忆道：“我记得很清楚，《第五元素》在戛纳首映时，观众看法的确是两极分化”<ref>{{cite web | title = Summer Blockbusters – Your Best and Worst | last = Kermode | first = Mark | date = 2012-08-28 | work = BBC | accessdate = 2014-12-10 | archivedate = 2014-12-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141210142800/http://www.bbc.co.uk/blogs/legacy/markkermode/2012/08/summer_blockbusters_-_your_bes.html | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/blogs/legacy/markkermode/2012/08/summer_blockbusters_-_your_bes.html | deadurl = no}}</ref>。斯蒂芬·卡斯（{{lang|en|Stephen Cass}}）在《[[发现_(杂志)|发现]]》上把本片评为{{lang|en|[[Hulu|Hulu]]}}订阅电影中科幻类的第3位，他写道：“人们对《第五元素》似乎不是喜欢就是讨厌……豪华的视觉效果和布鲁斯·威利斯、米拉·乔沃维奇以及加里·奥德曼的娱乐表演让这部电影值得一看”<ref>{{cite web | url = http://blogs.discovermagazine.com/sciencenotfiction/2008/12/24/5-best-science-fiction-movies-on-hulu-3-the-fifth-element/#.VIhZzby_M5N | title = 5 Best Science Fiction Movies on Hulu: #3, The Fifth Element | last = Cass | first = Stephen | date = 2008-12-24 | work = Discover | accessdate = 2014-12-10 | archive-date = 2014-10-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141023115614/http://blogs.discovermagazine.com/sciencenotfiction/2008/12/24/5-best-science-fiction-movies-on-hulu-3-the-fifth-element/#.VIhZzby_M5N | dead-url = no }}</ref>。有评价称本片已经达到“实在太糟、糟到很好”的境界，梅雷迪思·韦尔纳（{{lang|en|Meredith Woerner}}）在{{lang|en|[[io9|io9]]}}网站上评选“历史上20部最糟糕的科幻电影”，《第五元素》榜上有名<ref>{{cite web | url = http://io9.com/5052003/the-20-best-worst-science-fiction-movies-of-all-time | title = The 20 Best Worst Science Fiction Movies of All Time | last = Woerner | first = Meredith | date = 2008-09-18 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140815091851/http://io9.com/5052003/the-20-best-worst-science-fiction-movies-of-all-time | work = io9 | accessdate = 2014-12-10 | archivedate = 2014-08-15 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。2007年，[[视觉效果协会|视觉效果协会]]评选历史上最有影响的50部视觉效果电影，《第五元素》同《[[梦游小人国|梦游小人国]]》（{{lang|en|''Darby O'Gill and the Little People''}}）并列排在第50名<ref>{{cite web|title=The Visual Effects Society Unveils '50 Most Influential Visual Effects Films of All Time' |date=2007-05-11 |work=Studio Daily |accessdate=2014-12-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140102035854/http://www.studiodaily.com/2007/05/the-visual-effects-society-unveils-a%C2%A2aeaoe50-most-influential-visual-effects-films-of-all-timea%C2%A2aea%C2%9D/ |archivedate=2014-01-02 |deadurl=no |url=http://www.studiodaily.com/2007/05/the-visual-effects-society-unveils-a%C2%A2aeaoe50-most-influential-visual-effects-films-of-all-timea%C2%A2aea%C2%9D/ }}</ref>。

威利斯在1999年接受采访时予以本片好评，表示电影拍摄过程乐趣十足<ref name="special" />。塔克和乔沃维奇也在接受采访时对参拍本片的过程以及与贝松合作的经历赞不绝口，这些采访内容收录在电影的旗舰版{{lang|en|[[DVD|DVD]]}}中，乔沃维奇还称赞贝松是她合作过的第一位“真是了不起”的导演<ref>{{cite AV media | year = 2005 | title = The Fifth Element – Ultimate Edition | medium = DVD | publisher = Columbia TriStar Motion Picture Group}}</ref>。2014年，加里·奥德曼在接受采访时表示他不喜欢《第五元素》：“哦不，我实在受不了”<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.playboy.com/articles/gary-oldman-playboy-interview | title = Playboy Interview: Gary Oldman | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141121120108/http://www.playboy.com/articles/gary-oldman-playboy-interview | deadurl = yes | last = Hochman | first = David | date = 2014-06-25 | website = Playboy | accessdate = 2014-12-10 | archivedate = 2014年11月21日 | df =  }}</ref>。他还曾在2011年声称，自己出演《第五元素》从一定程度上是因为吕克·贝松登门邀请，并且还为自己执导的电影《[[切勿吞食|切勿吞食]]》（{{lang|en|''Nil by Mouth''}}）注资<ref>{{cite web|archivedate=2014-10-28 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141028012257/http://www.liveforfilms.com/2011/09/28/gary-oldman-a-life-in-pictures-bafta/ |url=http://www.liveforfilms.com/2011/09/28/gary-oldman-a-life-in-pictures-bafta/ |title=Gary Oldman "A Life In Pictures" @ BAFTA |last=Hamm |first=Matt |date=2011-09-28 |website=Live For Films |accessdate=2014-12-10 }}</ref>。

电影上映后，[[亚历山卓·尤杜洛斯基|亚历山卓·尤杜洛斯基]]和尚·吉罗对贝松提出起诉，声称《第五元素》剽窃了他们的漫画作品。吉罗的诉讼要求包括不正当竞争赔偿1310万[[欧元|欧元]]，损害赔偿和利息共900万欧元，还要求对电影经营净收入分成2到5个百分点；尤杜洛斯基则要求70万欧元赔偿。法庭之后认为电影只采用了漫画中“细微的片段”<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.toutenbd.com/article.php3?id_article=697 | title = Moebius perd son procès contre Besson | date = 2004-05-28 | work = ToutenBD | accessdate = 2014-12-10 | archivedate = 2014年10月28日 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141028025038/http://www.toutenbd.com/article.php3?id_article=697 | df =  }}</ref>，并且吉罗在作出指控前还曾接受贝松的聘请，因此驳回了起诉<ref name="av" />。

1997年，由[[特里·比森|特里·比森]]（{{lang|en|Terry Bisson}}）执笔，[[哈珀柯林斯|哈珀柯林斯]]出版的电影同名改编小说发行<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.worldcat.org/title/fifth-element-a-novel/oclc/36966341?referer=brief_results | title = The fifth element : a novel | work = WorldCat | accessdate = 2014-12-10 | archivedate = 2014-12-10 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141210152124/http://www.worldcat.org/wcpa/servlet/org.oclc.lac.ui.ajax.ServiceServlet?wcoclcnum=36966341&start_holding=&pgload=&serviceCommand=holdingsdata}}</ref><ref>{{cite book | last = Bisson | first = Terry | title = The Fifth Element: A Novel | year = 1997 | publisher = HarperPrism | isbn = 978-0-06-105838-7}}</ref>。电影上映后曾有传言称其后会拍摄[[续集|续集]]，片名暂定《影子先生》（{{lang|en|''Mr. Shadow''}}），但贝松在2011年接受采访时表示，他根本没有计划过要为《第五元素》拍摄续集，也没有这样的想法<ref>{{cite web|deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141110134758/http://news.moviefone.com/2011/08/26/luc-besson-reflects-on-his-female-leads-and-explains-why-a-fift/ |archivedate=2014-11-10 |url=http://news.moviefone.com/2011/08/26/luc-besson-reflects-on-his-female-leads-and-explains-why-a-fift/ |title=Luc Besson Reflects on His Female Leads and Explains Why a 'Fifth Element' Sequel Will Never Happen |work=Moviefone |first=Mike |last=Ryan |date=2011-08-26 |accessdate=2014-12-10 }}</ref>。

1998年，[[动视|动视]]制作了《第五元素》的同名[[电子游戏|电子游戏]]，并分为{{lang|en|[[PlayStation_(品牌)|PlayStation]]}}和{{lang|en|[[个人电脑|PC]]}}两种版本。其中{{lang|en|PlayStation}}总体评价欠佳<ref>{{cite web | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141110064810/http://www.gamerankings.com/ps/197318-the-fifth-element/index.html | url = http://www.gamerankings.com/ps/197318-the-fifth-element/index.html | title = The Fifth Element for PlayStation | work = GameRankings | accessdate = 2014-12-10 | archivedate = 2014-11-10}}</ref>，不过{{lang|en|PC}}版本的情况就要好得多<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamerankings.com/pc/198963-the-fifth-element/index.html | title = The Fifth Element | work = GameRankings | accessdate = 2014-12-10 | archivedate = 2014-11-10 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141110074550/http://www.gamerankings.com/pc/198963-the-fifth-element/index.html}}</ref>。劳伦·菲尔德（{{lang|en|Lauren Fielder}}）在《[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]》上表示，{{lang|en|Playstation}}版《第五元素》“很可能是我玩过最烂的游戏”<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamespot.com/reviews/fifth-element-the-review/1900-2546460/ | title = Fifth Element, The Review (PS) | publisher = GameSpot | last = Fielder | first = Lauren | date = 1998-10-21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141210155521/http://www.gamespot.com/reviews/fifth-element-the-review/1900-2546460/ | accessdate = 2014-12-10 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-12-10}}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[IGN|IGN]]}}的道格·佩里（{{lang|en|Doug Perry}}）评价：“拿出《[[古墓丽影系列|古墓丽影]]》，加上莉露和无聊的谜题就成了《第五元素》”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://au.ign.com/articles/1998/10/02/fifth-element |title=Fifth Element |last=Perry |first=Doug |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141110074006/http://www.ign.com/articles/1998/10/02/fifth-element%2A |date=1998-10-01 |work=IGN |accessdate=2014-12-10 |archivedate=2014年11月10日 |deadurl=yes |df= }}</ref>。2001年，根据本片改编的赛车游戏《纽约赛车》（{{lang|en|''New York Race''}}）面世<ref name="eurogamer">{{cite web | url = http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/r_nyrace | title = NY Race | last = Taylor | first = Martin | date = 2001-11-15 | work = Eurogamer | accessdate = 2014-12-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141110061317/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/r_nyrace | archivedate = 2014年11月10日 | deadurl = yes | df =  }}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]}}网站给予该游戏的评分为6（最高为10），称“《纽约赛车》是款散发出格调的有趣街机小游戏，但这种乐趣只能持续很短暂的时间，很快你就会感到厌倦”<ref name="eurogamer" />。

== 荣誉 ==
《第五元素》在[[第70届奥斯卡金像奖|第70届奥斯卡金像奖]]角逐中获[[奥斯卡最佳音效剪辑奖|音效剪辑奖]]提名<ref name="Oscars1998">{{cite web | url = http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/70th-winners.html | title = The 70th Academy Awards (1998) Nominees and Winners | accessdate = 2014-03-30 | work = Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences | publisher = AMPAS | archivedate = 2013-12-24 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131224032304/http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/70th-winners.html}}</ref>，并获1998年金卷轴奖最佳音效剪辑奖提名<ref>{{cite journal | date = 1998-03-09 | title = Mark Mangini | url = http://markmangini.com/Mark_Mangini/Resume_files/Hollywood%20Reporter.pdf | magazine = The Hollywood Reporter | page = C-11 | issn = 0018-3660 | accessdate = 2014-12-11 | archivedate = 2014-11-09 | format = [[PDF|PDF]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141109175104/http://markmangini.com/Mark_Mangini/Resume_files/Hollywood%20Reporter.pdf | deadurl = yes }}</ref>，但最终双双不敌《[[泰坦尼克号_(1997年电影)|泰坦尼克号]]》。电影获得了[[英国电影学院奖|英国电影学院奖]]最佳特技视觉效果奖<ref>{{cite web | url = http://awards.bafta.org/award/1998/film/achievement-in-special-visual-effects | title = Achievement in Special Visual Effects in 1998 | work = British Academy of Film and Television Arts | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141109175340/http://awards.bafta.org/award/1998/film/achievement-in-special-visual-effects | archivedate = 2014-11-09 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2014-12-11}}</ref><ref name="nyawards">{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141109175239/http://www.nytimes.com/movies/movie/154944/The-Fifth-Element/awards | url = http://www.nytimes.com/movies/movie/154944/The-Fifth-Element/awards | title = The Fifth Element (1997) | work = The New York Times | accessdate = 2014-12-11 | archivedate = 2014-11-09 | deadurl = no}}</ref>和卢米埃奖最佳导演奖<ref>{{cite web | url = http://movies.msn.com/movies/movie-awards-and-nominations/the-fifth-element/?ipp=15 | title = The Fifth Element:Awards & Nominations | work = MSN | accessdate = 2014-07-14 | archivedate = 2014-07-14 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714130446/http://movies.msn.com/movies/movie-awards-and-nominations/the-fifth-element/?ipp=15 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。影片获7项[[凯撒电影奖|凯撒电影奖]]提名，最终赢得了[[凯萨奖最佳导演奖|最佳导演]]<ref>{{cite web | url = http://variety.com/1998/film/news/resnais-seizes-7-cesars-1117468216/ | title = 'Chanson' big winner at top French kudos show | last = Williams | first = Michael | date = 1998-03-01 | work = Variety | accessdate = 2014-12-11 | archive-date = 2014-12-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141225145633/http://variety.com/1998/film/news/resnais-seizes-7-cesars-1117468216/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>、最佳摄影和最佳艺术指导奖<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.academie-cinema.org/en/ceremony/awards.html | title = Palmares 1998 – 23th[sic] Cesar Award Ceremony | work = César Award | accessdate = 2014-12-11 | archivedate = 2014-10-18 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141018013409/http://www.academie-cinema.org/en/ceremony/awards.html | deadurl = yes }}</ref><ref name="nyawards" />。《第五元素》还获得1997年[[欧洲电影奖|欧洲电影奖]]年度电影<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.europeanfilmacademy.org/1997.95.0.html | title = 1997 | work = European Film Awards | accessdate = 2014-12-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141109174930/http://www.europeanfilmacademy.org/1997.95.0.html | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2014年11月9日 | df =  }}</ref>、[[雨果奖|雨果奖]][[雨果奖最佳戏剧呈现奖|最佳戏剧呈现]]<ref>{{cite web|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006111937/http://www.thehugoawards.org/hugo-history/1998-hugo-awards/ |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.thehugoawards.org/hugo-history/1998-hugo-awards/ |title=1998 Hugo Awards |work=Hugo Awards |accessdate=2014-12-11 |archivedate=2014-10-06 }}</ref>以及[[卫星奖|卫星奖]]最佳视觉效果奖提名<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.pressacademy.com/award_cat/1998/ | title = 1998 | work = International Press Academy | accessdate = 2014-12-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006092904/http://www.pressacademy.com/award_cat/1998/ | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-10-06}}</ref>。摄影师蒂埃里·阿伯加斯特因本片和《[[可人儿|可人儿]]》（{{lang|en|''She's So Lovely''}}）在1997年戛纳电影节上捧走了技术大奖<ref name="nyawards" />。电影还得到了4项[[土星奖|土星奖]]提名，分别是[[土星奖最佳科幻电影得奖列表|最佳科幻电影]]、最佳服装<ref>{{cite web | archivedate = 2014-10-21 | publisher = The New York Times Company | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141021081755/http://topics.nytimes.com/top/reference/timestopics/people/g/jean_paul_gaultier/index.html | url = http://topics.nytimes.com/top/reference/timestopics/people/g/jean_paul_gaultier/index.html | title = Jean Paul Gaultier | work = The New York Times | accessdate = 2014-12-11 | deadurl = no}}</ref>、最佳特技效果<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.kegfx.com/Keg/Awards/Index.html | title = VFX Awards | work = KEG FX | accessdate = 2014-12-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714202910/http://www.kegfx.com/Keg/Awards/Index.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-07-14}}</ref>和米拉·乔沃维奇的最佳女配角奖提名<ref name="post">{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141109172631/http://www.christianpost.com/news/milla-jovovich-blasts-summit-entertainment-for-ignoring-three-musketeers-58988/ | archivedate = 2014-11-09 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.christianpost.com/news/milla-jovovich-blasts-summit-entertainment-for-ignoring-three-musketeers-58988/ | title = Milla Jovovich Blasts Summit Entertainment for Ignoring 'Three Musketeers' | last = Justin | first = Sarachik | date = 2011-10-21 | work = The Christian Post | accessdate = 2014-12-11}}</ref>。片中乔沃维奇和孟加罗人打斗的场面获[[MTV电影大奖|MTV电影大奖]]最佳打斗奖提名<ref name="post" /><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.mtv.com/ontv/movieawards/1998/ | title = 1998 MTV Movie Awards | work = MTV | accessdate = 2014-12-11 | archivedate = 2014-10-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141007130146/http://www.mtv.com/ontv/movieawards/1998/ | deadurl = no}} Note: Click on the 'Winners' tab.</ref>，她还获得了[[大片娱乐奖|大片娱乐奖]]最佳女新人演员提名<ref>{{cite book | accessdate = 2014-12-11 | url = http://books.google.com.hk/books?id=rg0EAAAAMBAJ&pg=RA1-PA64&dq=%22blockbuster+entertainment+awards%22+nominees+billboard&hl=en&sa=X&ei=8zmYUaHkMof-iAfO3IGYBQ&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=%22blockbuster%20entertainment%20awards%22%20nominees%20billboard&f=false | title = 1996 Blockbuster Entertainment Awards Nominees Announced | date = 1998-01-17 | work = Billboard | page = 64}}</ref>。

除给予肯定的奖项外，乔沃维奇和克里斯·塔克还被[[金酸莓奖|金酸莓奖]]提名，其中乔沃维奇的提名奖项是[[金酸莓最差女配角奖|最差女配角奖]]，塔克则因本片和《[[超级轰天雷|超级轰天雷]]》（{{lang|en|''Money Talks''}}）而被提名最差新星奖<ref>{{cite web | url = http://razzies.com/asp/content/XcNewsPlus.asp?cmd=view&articleid=37 | title = 1997 Archive | date = 2000-08-23 | work = Golden Raspberry Award | accessdate = 2014-12-11 | archivedate = 2014-10-17 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141017202441/http://razzies.com/asp/content/XcNewsPlus.asp?cmd=view&articleid=37 }}</ref>。

